{"type": "article", "id": 22511, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-02-19T07:49:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 3875, "name": "包装设计"}, {"id": 2976, "name": "灯饰"}, {"id": 23639, "name": "himmee"}, {"id": 23640, "name": "Stumpf Studio"}, {"id": 23641, "name": "Anna New York"}, {"id": 23642, "name": "Super Magic Friend"}, {"id": 23643, "name": "silvia ceñal"}, {"id": 23644, "name": "Roger Persson"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 44, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703120035iMcpT3fJvmXSEz0l.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>forêt by Silvia Ceñal </h2>\n<p>这张木桌来自西班牙设计师 Silvia Ceñal，它的特殊之处在于桌腿与铰接支座之间的关节设计。设计师称灵感源于法国朗德森林里的巨松，它的树干上有粗壮垂直相交的枝条。对应到这张桌子，较粗的桌腿就是树干，两根较细的横梁支撑则是上枝条，给人轻盈而优雅的视觉感受，<a href=\"http://www.silviacenal.com/#/foret-table/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154116necMlYSNH0KLxUZm.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57212714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154117AE342rdqpUZkRDFI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72738386\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154117Eqnc2A38TUrbWaIZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.22371638\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154118m8yWqxMhvGJbfsjS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.84474328\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154118ZIrp2JblKUgyWPqs.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.00488998\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Connect system by Swedese &amp; Roger Persson</h2>\n<p>瑞典设计品牌 Swedese 和设计师 Roger Persson 发布了一组模块化的家具，分为正方形或者正圆形两种沙发坐垫，都可以随意拼起来。在选色上使用了黄、蓝、绿、棕等自然的颜色，带给人格外的清新自然。正方形的沙发可以拼成一个大的坐垫组，其中有一块是橡木桌面，而圆形坐垫像是分散在其中的绿叶。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071541188McI5LABRi2bwnCD.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.84615385\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071541191TQotP367mAbh2l8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154119kNWweTMFbiZPJr8o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154120ylA3eiRdYH0qvSh1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154120Mdsu98xRpn7zyDmB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>loop lamp by himmee</h2>\n<p>这盏像圆环一样的桌灯来自芬兰设计工作室 himmee，最早出现在 2009 年的米兰家具展上，最近完成了工业化并出现在斯德哥尔摩家具展上。它其实是铝制的，光源在环状灯内壁的上半侧。点亮后整盏灯就像是一根舞动的带子，很有意境。有黑白两色可选，售价 419 欧元，<a href=\"http://himmee.com/product/loop/\">这里是购买链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154121C1uB5A0WGva2r4yo.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.49633252\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154121qh6ws1dU9JKp5A8M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61735941\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154122sSrVzpixZRe3At4u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70782396\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154122VgNY5lDp0CvnEqL8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61124694\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Bumble cutting board by Stumpf Studio</h2>\n<p>这是一款折叠砧板，以方便将切好的菜倒进锅内。它的原理其实很简单，使用两块同样大小的木板，在侧面装上钢夹。它也有拍压一些菜的功能。也许对于小厨房来说，一个折叠的砧板也是一个节约空间的办法。有 3 种深浅颜色可选，售价 42 美元起，<a href=\"http://shop.stumpfstudio.com\">这里是购买链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154122N2mApjhlfSD10O7x.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154123w6IdWH5j39PDkX1t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154124TqAPchQfU4jMXwHs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154124ut5BYiWRg79y6wEO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154125VNuiB3qmCJbSX21A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Amare Serving Set by Anna New York</h2>\n<p>这是一组调料瓶，来自美国女设计师 Anna Rabinowicz 自创的品牌 Anna New York。她使用了金属和大理石的经典搭配，圆筒形的瓶身上放着半圆大理石盖子，不同材料之间在颜色、纹路和质感上都有一个反差，但维持了巧妙的平衡，带有古典色彩。可以选择不锈钢灰、玫瑰金和金色三种，售价 185 美元起，<a href=\"http://www.annanewyork.com/collections/tabletop/products/amare-serving-set\">这里是购买链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154125RUvs4Dq6kA20VjQX.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.77314815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154126VRMyl698aStqnNd2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.93833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154126jcRstnkl32TMdKhx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.295\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154127nl8TOeyaNKJEPUVI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.77333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154127RngiS9K2dzPj0mco.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.77333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Astronut® by Super Magic Friend</h2>\n<p>这是墨西哥的平面设计工作室 Super Magic Friend 为墨西哥一家新开的面包店设计的整体形象和包装，logo 就是一个被咬了一口的甜甜圈。紫色的甜甜圈上分布着彩色的小糖针，它们又分散到了整体的包装上，带给人一种梦幻的感觉，似乎已经尝到了甜甜圈带给人的美好。如果仔细看，logo 也像是一个带宇航员的水晶球或是一只眼睛，很有趣。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154128ayYuQUXFeL2pEKAz.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6712963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154128ChV0xOeBt5lHzE9p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67592593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071541280WFhjtHXSoGiAOKE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154129m9qk5PYzhridHa7F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154130jEZc0kL2YTBbusr5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67685185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154130b4K3qhxsiMELY0Nr.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154131G207FNbLPXsl5ctq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67407407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}